Notebook[{

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["Overlap Calculation of Different Input Modes", "Title",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9682338627642827`*^9, 
  3.968233878976967*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"21999871-4b3e-4af6-ba01-\
b4ca2fbe89c4"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Here, we calculate the overlap between different input modes to our coveted \
Knot Sorter. We start by defining the algebraic wavefunctions of the Trefoil, \
Cinquefoil, and Figure-8 knots.  They are given as (from our Knot Sorter \
overleaf)\n",
